text: Rudolf Rieger (5 January 1916 - 13 March 1996) was an Austrian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Austrian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Austria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Mödling District Category:Sportspeople from Lower Austria
